text.section:
The cabinet may revoke or suspend any certification issued pursuant to this section upon proof that the certified person has:
Knowingly violated the provisions of this chapter or the regulations of the cabinet;
Practiced fraud or deception in applying for or obtaining a certificate;
Is incompetent to install on-site sewage disposal systems;
Permitted the certification to be used directly or indirectly by another to install on-site sewage disposal systems; or
Is guilty of other unprofessional or dishonorable conduct of a character likely to deceive or defraud the public.
